ef4c59ef-e10e-40ca-b102-3aff6510b337.title: 'Gummy'
ef4c59ef-e10e-40ca-b102-3aff6510b337.text: Rock, Paper, Scissors. Can't you tell?

c5670cd5-fb29-4818-bfd7-36b0dce40965.title: <player>
c5670cd5-fb29-4818-bfd7-36b0dce40965.text: It was more of a rhetorical question.

230b5dfa-93af-4714-b093-a4c26419fdc9.title: <player>
230b5dfa-93af-4714-b093-a4c26419fdc9.text:
Ah, come on. You know you want to give me free
stuff.

952b0a49-8426-4cf0-8498-8ac0fd33a59b.title: 'Gummy'
952b0a49-8426-4cf0-8498-8ac0fd33a59b.text: Stop bothering me, can't you see I'm busy!

af238d80-f976-4803-b36d-d60b47126ac1.title: 'Gummy'
af238d80-f976-4803-b36d-d60b47126ac1.text:
Okay, okay. The other day I was drying my clothes on
a line down by the shore. A storm hit and some of my
clothing went missing.

fb9eb1c0-537a-4e97-b34f-927b6d7859a8.title: <player>
fb9eb1c0-537a-4e97-b34f-927b6d7859a8.text: Likely story. Sure you weren't skinny dipping?

648950c4-3328-4b83-97bb-f5f1854cd90d.title: 'Gummy'
648950c4-3328-4b83-97bb-f5f1854cd90d.text:
Just go look and leave me be! Search around the tower
and you may find them.

3bfb66f6-6c50-41ff-a505-11b3d3de2e9d.title: 'Gummy'
3bfb66f6-6c50-41ff-a505-11b3d3de2e9d.text:
It's a draw at the moment. First it was best of three,
then it was best of five.

d3c746f7-913b-43c2-852a-2ea41e8c839d.title: 'Gummy'
d3c746f7-913b-43c2-852a-2ea41e8c839d.text: Best of a hundred and one.
